ActFirst Nations Goods and Services Tax Act
SubjectOrder Amending Schedule 1 to the First Nations Goods and Services Tax Act, No. 2011-1 (Blueberry River First Nations)
PrecisOrder Amending SCHEDULE 1 TO THE FIRST NATIONS GOODS AND SERVICES TAX ACT, NO. 2011-1 (BLUEBERRY RIVER FIRST NATIONS) in order to add the name of the Blueberry River First Nations, the name of its governing body and the description of the lands where the Blueberry River First Nations goods and services tax law could apply.
